code: public void setExpression(ExpressionDefinition expression) {     // favour using the helper to set the expression as it can unwrap some unwanted builders when using Java DSL     if (expression instanceof Expression) {         this.expression = ExpressionNodeHelper.toExpressionDefinition((Expression) expression).     } else if (expression instanceof Predicate) {         this.expression = ExpressionNodeHelper.toExpressionDefinition((Predicate) expression).     } else {         this.expression = expression.     } }
